{"componentChunkName":"component---src-template-post-tsx","path":"/intellij-포커스/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"nodes":[{"fields":{"slug":"/intellij-자동완성/"},"timeToRead":2,"frontmatter":{"title":"[IntelliJ] 자동완성","series":"IntelliJ"}},{"fields":{"slug":"/intellij-리팩토링/"},"timeToRead":4,"frontmatter":{"title":"[IntelliJ] 리팩토링","series":"IntelliJ"}},{"fields":{"slug":"/intellij-디버깅/"},"timeToRead":2,"frontmatter":{"title":"[IntelliJ] 디버깅","series":"IntelliJ"}},{"fields":{"slug":"/intellij-Git-Github/"},"timeToRead":3,"frontmatter":{"title":"[IntelliJ] Git&Github","series":"IntelliJ"}},{"fields":{"slug":"/intellij-플러그인/"},"timeToRead":1,"frontmatter":{"title":"[IntelliJ] 플러그인","series":"IntelliJ"}},{"fields":{"slug":"/intellij-소개/"},"timeToRead":3,"frontmatter":{"title":"[IntelliJ] 소개","series":"IntelliJ"}},{"fields":{"slug":"/intellij-코드-Edit/"},"timeToRead":6,"frontmatter":{"title":"[IntelliJ] 코드 Edit","series":"IntelliJ"}},{"fields":{"slug":"/intellij-포커스/"},"timeToRead":3,"frontmatter":{"title":"[IntelliJ] 포커스","series":"IntelliJ"}},{"fields":{"slug":"/intellij-검색/"},"timeToRead":3,"frontmatter":{"title":"[IntelliJ] 검색","series":"IntelliJ"}}]},"markdownRemark":{"id":"bfe9a36c-5079-548f-9c01-b72e58b1c7bb","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1024px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"banner\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/7f3c4c668ea513e0950e70c83ed0a8d8/2bef9/banner.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7f3c4c668ea513e0950e70c83ed0a8d8/6f3f2/banner.png 256w,\n/static/7f3c4c668ea513e0950e70c83ed0a8d8/01e7c/banner.png 512w,\n/static/7f3c4c668ea513e0950e70c83ed0a8d8/2bef9/banner.png 1024w,\n/static/7f3c4c668ea513e0950e70c83ed0a8d8/c1b63/banner.png 1200w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>해당 포스팅은 인프런의 <a href=\"https://inf.run/doaZn\">IntelliJ를 시작하시는 분들을 위한 IntelliJ 가이드</a> 강의를 참조하여 작성한 글입니다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>포커스 에디터</h2>\n<p>이번에는 포커스 관련 단축키를 알아보도록 하겠다. 아래의 코드를 가지고 한번 알아보자.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-java line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token keyword\">package</span> <span class=\"token namespace\">me<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>sungbin<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>chap2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">FocusEditor</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">focus</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> s <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"안녕하세요. 반갑습니다. IntelliJ IDEA Ultimate\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token class-name\">System</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>out<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">println</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">page1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token class-name\">System</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>out<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">println</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"간격을 넓히기 위한 코드1\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token class-name\">System</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>out<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">println</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"간격을 넓히기 위한 코드2\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">page2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token class-name\">System</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>out<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">println</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"간격을 넓히기 위한 코드1\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token class-name\">System</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>out<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">println</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"간격을 넓히기 위한 코드2\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\